Subject: Current Focal Point

Description: Compact attention-direction packet to reload after context compression.

& [CurrentFocalPoint] is the live re-entry seed for active focus
  + [status] is active
  + [renewal_reason] is preserve focused attention across context compression
  + [focus_subject] is primed Codex CLI LM Studio worker passed minimal no-tools SOP smoke
  + [focus_mode] is mixed_focus
  + [executive_drive] is use the successful primer-first stdin_only smoke test to define the next local-worker readiness gate: primer comprehension schema, then tiny framework excerpt, then non-mutating task
